org.sipdroid.sipua

Class RegisterAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sipdroid.sipua.RegisterAgent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SubscriberDialogListener, TransactionClientListener

    public class RegisterAgent
extends java.lang.Object
implements TransactionClientListener, SubscriberDialogListener
    Register User Agent. It registers (one time or periodically) a contact address with a registrar server.
